            <p><font size="3"><br>
            3. 学会・セミナー等対外発表</font></p>
            <ul style="list-style-type : none">
			  <li><font size="3"><b>(21)An Asymptotic and Perturbative Expansion Approach in Finance</b><br>
              Global Derivatives Trading & Risk Management 2014<br>
